01:23:48,792 --> 01:23:52,830
So, what next? Hmm?

1386
01:23:52,831 --> 01:23:54,870
A wander around the Marais?

1387
01:23:54,871 --> 01:23:57,535
Hmm, that would be nice.

1388
01:23:57,992 --> 01:24:03,070
But... I was thinking of something
a little more adventurous.

1389
01:24:03,071 --> 01:24:07,023
Adventurous? Marvellous.
When are we leaving?

1390
01:24:07,791 --> 01:24:10,215
What about right now?

1391
01:24:10,870 --> 01:24:12,815
OK?

1392
01:24:13,830 --> 01:24:16,029
You see, I...

1393
01:24:16,030 --> 01:24:19,669
I know a man.
I know a man with a boat.

1394
01:24:19,670 --> 01:24:21,309
- Oh, you do, do you?
- Yes.

1395
01:24:21,310 --> 01:24:23,658
Yes? What?

1396
01:24:24,229 --> 01:24:26,869
Where? No! This?

1397
01:24:26,870 --> 01:24:28,748
Oh, my God! She's beautiful.

1398
01:24:28,749 --> 01:24:30,790
- Kate, you did it. You did it!
- I did it!

1399
01:24:30,790 --> 01:24:32,747
- You bought us a boat!
- I did it!

1400
01:24:32,749 --> 01:24:34,667
Don't fall in. Don't
fall in the Seine.

1401
01:24:34,668 --> 01:24:37,428
Oh, my God, she's gorgeous!

1402
01:24:37,429 --> 01:24:39,948
She is gorgeous. You are gorgeous!

1403
01:24:39,949 --> 01:24:42,013
I love you!

